Package net.replaceitem.reconfigure.config.serialization

Class TypeAdapter<T,M extends Intermediary<?>>

java.lang.Object
net.replaceitem.reconfigure.config.serialization.TypeAdapter<T,M>
Type Parameters:
T - Type of the property
M - Type of the intermediary type
public abstract class TypeAdapter<T,M extends Intermediary<?>> extends Object
Converts a typed property value to and from an Intermediary type for serialization. PropertyBuilders will attach the correct adapter to the Property when building. The Intermediary will then be used by the Marshaller to convert to a Serializer specific type.
